BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-08-1800-studiotwothree@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260628T120605Z
DTSTART:20260708T180000
DTEND:20260708T210000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing - 7/8
LOCATION:Studio Two Three\, 109 W 15th St Richmond\, VA 23224
DESCRIPTION:3-hour figure drawing workshop with nude model. Instructor Carter Helmandollar leads gestural poses to longer poses. Bring your own drawing/painting/sculpting materials. No photography permitted.\\n\\nCost: $20\\n\\nRegister: https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-78
URL:https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-78
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-13-1000-manchester-studios-rva@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260628T120605Z
DTSTART:20260713T100000
DTEND:20260713T173000
SUMMARY:The Alchemy Of Expression – Portrait Sculpture Workshop
LOCATION:Manchester Studios RVA\, 1300 West Main Street\, Richmond\, Virginia 23220
DESCRIPTION:Two-week intensive portrait sculpture workshop (July 13–17 and 20–24). Covers skull anatomy\, muscles\, facial features\, and creating a likeness from a live model using Classical Realism observational techniques. All skill levels welcome. All materials and model fees included.\\n\\nCost: $1600\\n\\nRegister: https://manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops/
URL:https://manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops/
END:VEVENT
